        {
          "title": {
            "_text": "Melonbooks宣告2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款"
          },
          "link": {
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30723"
          },
          "comments": {
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30723#respond"
          },
          "dc:creator": {
            "_cdata": "萌朧雪猴"
          },
          "pubDate": {
            "_text": "Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:28:07 +0000"
          },
          "category": [
            {
              "_cdata": "話題情報"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "Melonbooks"
            }
          ],
          "guid": {
            "_attributes": {
              "isPermaLink": "false"
            },
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/?p=30723"
          },
          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>以同人誌為中心，專門販賣各種漫畫、動畫BD、遊戲等商品的店鋪「Melonbooks」，11月8日正式公告，將自2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30723\">Melonbooks宣告2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">以同人誌為中心，專門販賣各種漫畫、動畫BD、遊戲等商品的店鋪「Melonbooks」，11月8日正式公告，將自2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"780\" height=\"217\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002008/melonbooksstopvisa01.webp\" alt=\"melonbooksstopvisa01\" class=\"wp-image-30724\" title=\"Melonbooks宣告2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款 1\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002008/melonbooksstopvisa01.webp 780w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002008/melonbooksstopvisa01-300x83.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002008/melonbooksstopvisa01-768x214.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002008/melonbooksstopvisa01-750x209.webp 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">在日本官方正式公告中提到，直到2024年12月18日，信用卡仍能使用JCB、AmericanExpress與VISA支付方式；不過2024年12月19日開始，信用卡就只能使用JCB、AmericanExpress。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"956\" height=\"655\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002011/melonbooksstopvisa02.webp\" alt=\"melonbooksstopvisa02\" class=\"wp-image-30725\" title=\"Melonbooks宣告2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款 2\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002011/melonbooksstopvisa02.webp 956w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002011/melonbooksstopvisa02-300x206.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002011/melonbooksstopvisa02-768x526.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002011/melonbooksstopvisa02-750x514.webp 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 956px) 100vw, 956px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">另外針對Melonbooks實體店鋪的信用卡支付，則是暫定會自2024年12月中旬後陸續回復VISA/Master，同時也規劃「メロブ店舗決済(Melob Store Payment)」的新支付方式。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-724x1024.webp\" alt=\"melonbooksstopvisa03\" class=\"wp-image-30726\" title=\"Melonbooks宣告2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款 3\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-724x1024.webp 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-212x300.webp 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-768x1086.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-1086x1536.webp 1086w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-1448x2048.webp 1448w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-750x1061.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-1140x1613.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002018/melonbooksstopvisa03-scaled.webp 1810w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">而<a href=\"https://www.plurk.com/p/3gib55u61v\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.plurk.com/p/3gib55u61v\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Melonbooks繁中plurk</a>也公開了此一訊息。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"526\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002021/melonbooksstopvisa04.webp\" alt=\"melonbooksstopvisa04\" class=\"wp-image-30727\" title=\"Melonbooks宣告2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款 4\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002021/melonbooksstopvisa04.webp 526w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/09002021/melonbooksstopvisa04-300x179.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 526px) 100vw, 526px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">目前未知Melonbooks於12月19日後，何時會恢復通販可使用VISA/Master信用卡付款。 </p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.melonbooks.co.jp/news/index.php?news_id=914\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.melonbooks.co.jp/news/index.php?news_id=914\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">官方公告</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30723\">Melonbooks宣告2024年12月19日起 停止VISA/Master信用卡付款</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
