              "_cdata": "龍杰國際"
            }
          ],
          "guid": {
            "_attributes": {
              "isPermaLink": "false"
            },
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/?p=30691"
          },
          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>玩具模型品牌代理經銷商「龍杰國際」，公開「2024龍杰國際精品玩具展」將於新竹遠東巨城舉辦，並同步公開預計販售商品資訊。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30691\">2024龍杰國際精品玩具展將於新竹遠東巨城舉辦 將販售戰爭之影人馬幻紫、狙擊獵狐雪白等限定商品</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">玩具模型品牌代理經銷商「龍杰國際」，公開「2024龍杰國際精品玩具展」將於新竹遠東巨城舉辦，並同步公開預計販售商品資訊。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"299\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-1024x299.webp\" alt=\"2024toymaxfebigcitynews01\" class=\"wp-image-30692\" title=\"2024龍杰國際精品玩具展將於新竹遠東巨城舉辦 將販售戰爭之影人馬幻紫、狙擊獵狐雪白等限定商品 5\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-1024x299.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-300x88.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-768x224.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-1536x448.webp 1536w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-2048x597.webp 2048w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-750x219.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07173310/2024toymaxfebigcitynews01-1140x333.webp 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">此次限定商品涵蓋機娘組裝模型，以下為相關商品清單：</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Moshow 模壽</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">金色限定版-湖中騎士</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">核能矩陣</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">戰爭之影-人馬幻紫配色</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">狙擊獵狐-雪白色獵狐</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Heatboys 火仔</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">夢幻金米奇</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">夢幻藍米奇</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">夢幻粉米奇</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">金色忍者龜-拉菲爾</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">靈機魂</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">環太平洋-戰損版赤紅</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">庫造積木</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">限定版 &#8211; 魔化張飛</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://img.moelong.com/images/2024toymaxfebigcitynews/2024toymaxfebigcitynews02.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"2024龍杰國際精品玩具展將於新竹遠東巨城舉辦 將販售戰爭之影人馬幻紫、狙擊獵狐雪白等限定商品 6\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「2024龍杰國際精品玩具展」，從2024年11月8日－11月21日，於新竹遠東巨城購物中心5F創藝廳舉辦。 </p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TOYMAX88\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/TOYMAX88\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">龍杰國際 FB粉絲專頁</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30691\">2024龍杰國際精品玩具展將於新竹遠東巨城舉辦 將販售戰爭之影人馬幻紫、狙擊獵狐雪白等限定商品</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
