          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>由電擊文庫於2009年起出版發行小說單行本的《刀劍神域》，今11月7日14：55（日本時間），也是故事設定中正式破關「Sword Art Online」的時間，對此日本也釋出一系列的慶祝活動，包含動畫馬拉松直播、 Animate 池袋本店的「號外風廣告傳單」等。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30694\">現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">由電擊文庫於2009年起出版發行小說單行本的《刀劍神域》，今11月7日14：55（日本時間），也是故事設定中正式破關「Sword Art Online」的時間，對此日本也釋出一系列的慶祝活動，包含動畫馬拉松直播、&nbsp;Animate 池袋本店的「號外風廣告傳單」等。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration01\" class=\"wp-image-30695\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 12\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-212x300.jpg 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-750x1061.jpg 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">《刀劍神域》故事設定在公元 2022 年，配合「NERvGear」遊玩的次世代線上遊戲「Sword Art Online 刀劍神域〈SAO〉」，身為其中一名SAO的遊戲玩家──主角．桐人，卻意外與其餘九千多名玩家遭逢遇無法登出遊戲的異變。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://img.moelong.com/images/saosptwevent/saosptwevent67.jpg\" alt=\"saosptwevent67\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 13\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">在遊戲的舞台──巨大浮遊城堡「艾恩葛朗特」裡，桐人作為不與人組隊的獨行劍士，在遊戲中死亡便會實際身亡的嚴酷條件中，踏上完全攻略的道路。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://img.moelong.com/images/saosptwevent/saosptwevent12.jpg\" alt=\"saosptwevent12\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 14\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/11012\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/11012\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">此為「刀劍神域特展 2022」展場照</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">於故事中，桐人在&nbsp;2024 年 11 月 7 日 14：55（日本時間），終於順利通關「Sword Art Online 刀劍神域〈SAO〉」成功解放遊戲中存活的玩家，恰好也在今(7)日，故事時間軸迎來了現實的時間，因此也由官方規畫一系列慶祝活動。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration01\" class=\"wp-image-30695\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 12\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-212x300.jpg 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01-750x1061.jpg 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194523/saoclearcelebration01.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">2024年 11月7日 14時55分<br>ゲームはクリアされました――<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SAO%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%82%A2?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#SAOクリア</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/sao_anime?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#sao_anime</a><a href=\"https://t.co/sO2kkIRmHO\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/sO2kkIRmHO</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/4XPASV4IHY\" target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/4XPASV4IHY</a></p>&mdash; アニメ ソードアート・オンライン 公式 (@sao_anime) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sao_anime/status/1854402349412106416?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">November 7, 2024</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">日本除了動畫馬拉松直播外，也推出了<a href=\"https://online.aniplex.co.jp/SUcbnIdC\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://online.aniplex.co.jp/SUcbnIdC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">紀念週邊</a>、<a href=\"https://www.kadokawa.co.jp/product/200903000507/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.kadokawa.co.jp/product/200903000507/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">號外風廣告傳單</a>、特別影片等各種紀念活動。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"jeg_video_container jeg_video_content\"><iframe title=\"【NEWS】速報《ソードアート・オンライン》がクリア｜2024年11月7日 14時55分｜#SAOクリア\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gh1BHyBjfmg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">而動畫代理商木棉花也自11/7 09:30起，在台規劃《刀劍神域》<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UnNNICr4hf4\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UnNNICr4hf4\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SAO馬拉松直播</a>。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194528/saoclearcelebration02-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration02\" class=\"wp-image-30696\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 16\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194528/saoclearcelebration02-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194528/saoclearcelebration02-300x169.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194528/saoclearcelebration02-768x432.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194528/saoclearcelebration02-750x422.jpg 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194528/saoclearcelebration02-1140x641.jpg 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194528/saoclearcelebration02.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">雖然「NERvGear」沒有在2024年出現，不過筆者還是有高科技GSC X Cerevo 「High-Grade Electronic Toy 1/1電驅動聲光闡釋者」，可以在十分安全的狀態喊出「STARBURST STREAM(星光連流擊)」使出劍技，不用擔心有生命危險。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194531/saoclearcelebration03.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration03\" class=\"wp-image-30697\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 17\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194531/saoclearcelebration03.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194531/saoclearcelebration03-300x200.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194531/saoclearcelebration03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194531/saoclearcelebration03-750x500.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"335\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194534/saoclearcelebration04.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration04\" class=\"wp-image-30698\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 18\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194534/saoclearcelebration04.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194534/saoclearcelebration04-300x101.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194534/saoclearcelebration04-768x257.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194534/saoclearcelebration04-750x251.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194537/saoclearcelebration05.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration05\" class=\"wp-image-30699\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 19\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194537/saoclearcelebration05.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194537/saoclearcelebration05-300x200.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194537/saoclearcelebration05-768x512.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194537/saoclearcelebration05-750x500.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194541/saoclearcelebration06.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration06\" class=\"wp-image-30700\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 20\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194541/saoclearcelebration06.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194541/saoclearcelebration06-300x200.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194541/saoclearcelebration06-768x512.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194541/saoclearcelebration06-750x500.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">而《刀劍神域劇場版 &#8211; 序列爭戰》在台也自11月1日起，以日語原音、中文字幕重映2D 及 4DX版。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194545/saoclearcelebration07-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"saoclearcelebration07\" class=\"wp-image-30701\" title=\"現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開 21\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194545/saoclearcelebration07-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194545/saoclearcelebration07-212x300.jpg 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194545/saoclearcelebration07-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194545/saoclearcelebration07-750x1061.jpg 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/07194545/saoclearcelebration07.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">©2020 川原 礫/KADOKAWA/SAO-P Project</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">©2017 川原 礫／ＫＡＤＯＫＡＷＡ<br>アスキー・メディアワークス／SAO-A Project</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">©2016 川原 礫／ＫＡＤＯＫＡＷＡ<br>アスキー・メディアワークス刊／SAO MOVIE Project</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">©2014 川原 礫／ＫＡＤＯＫＡＷＡ<br>アスキー・メディアワークス刊／SAOⅡ Project ©川原 礫／<br>アスキー・メディアワークス／SAO Project</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30694\">現實終於趕上故事 《刀劍神域》2024年11月7日14時55分破關慶祝活動展開</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
